data.description: This charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home in Bridlewood Subdivision offers a cozy yet spacious living experience. The vaulted ceiling in the living room creates an inviting atmosphere, while the master bathroom boasts a luxurious jet tub for relaxation. The well-designed eat-in kitchen provides a convenient space for family meals and gatherings. The backyard offers ample space for entertaining. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your home! Seller is offering a $1500.00 painting allowance.
